data.description: Come check out this great home in the master planned community called Paloma get more home for the price of new. Seller will pay 5K of a buyer's closing costs. Also for a very savvy buyer there is an option to get the sellers assumable rate of 2.87%. Contact a Realtor for more details. This home is in the Heart of the NE located just 10min from the gates of Randolph AFB or FT SAM just a quick drive. The City of Converse is just a few miles on the outskirts of San Antonio save with No City Taxes, This location is very optimal with quick and easy commuting on IH10 to Downtown San Antonio with in a 15min drive or to South Austin in 45 mins.or New Braunfels in 15Min. Location is prime, schedule a tour of this wonderful home in this new community builder warranty available and transferable for extra piece of mind. M/I homes is one of the Top rated builders in this community.
